The following tables include summarized financial information of the obligor groups of debt issued by T-Mobile USA, Inc., Sprint,
Sprint Communications and Sprint Capital Corporation. The summarized financial information of each obligor group is presented
on a combined basis with balances and transactions within the obligor group eliminated. Investments in and the equity in earnings
of non-guarantor subsidiaries, which would otherwise be consolidated in accordance with U.S. GAAP, are excluded from the below
summarized financial information pursuant to SEC Regulation S-X Rule 13-01.
