provided pro forma financials prepared in accordance with Article 11. The pro forma results for the years ended December 31, 2020
and 2019 include the impact of several significant nonrecurring pro forma adjustments to previously reported operating results. The
pro forma adjustments are based on historically reported transactions by the respective companies. The pro forma results do not
include any anticipated synergies or other expected benefits of the acquisition.
